<li class='cover' id='bookCover_705418'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/705418.The_Limits_to_Growth"><img alt="The Limits to Growth: The 30-Year Update" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1390169255l/705418._SX98_.jpg" />
