<li class='cover' id='bookCover_56269264'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/56269264-the-dawn-of-everything"><img alt="The Dawn of Everything: A New History of Humanity" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1617072525l/56269264._SX98_.jpg" />
